{"tid":1745531,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"旺角區選投票站附近驚現近50枚汽油彈","createTime":"2019-11-22T09:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T09:32:56.000Z","uid":6261,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7167506810b18467c269dbe8b678780a4c0a5c52","tid":1745531,"uid":6261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:14:11.000Z","msg":"旺角區選投票站附近驚現近50枚汽油彈 警查來源動機<br />\n<br />\n現場是洗衣街239號旁邊一條橫巷，警方下午約3時接獲市民報案，指上址發現一批汽油彈。警員到場，將現場圍封調查。經點算後，初步證實有4盆汽油彈，每盆有10多枚，警方在場另檢獲多個空樽及仍未入樽的汽油。<br />\n<br />\n涉案現場對面是界限街1號體育館，周日將作為區議會選舉投票站，警方正追查該批汽油彈的來源及使用動機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2QGJo2o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QGJo2o&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=3f76ca61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2QGJo2o</a><br />\n<br />\n又出招"},{"pid":"8d7b5e6bd8e840eb1f85f5e02a6de64955a85844","tid":1745531,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:16:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60beee8fa953b0398c81c298ca4acf02f670da3a","tid":1745531,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:19:35.000Z","msg":"政府取消區選前奏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5f7a042ef78d9d4e1ab0587c1779459604f6c5","tid":1745531,"uid":265179,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:20:15.000Z","msg":"以前一聽到汽油彈個名就好嚇人, 而家聽黎好似叉燒包咁好平常"},{"pid":"bccf9a1436721258d5ad1459b19d5f622cf677f7","tid":1745531,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:24:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00fae9e0288eed550b902481ba3ad04f402510c1","tid":1745531,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:25:45.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=9ff1751e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=e7f85e69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=f836fa86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylrXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=fbf3df88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxRo2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxRo2R.jpg&h=1a7a9910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8fcedecf4ced4792f35fc828771e3848b4f3f98","tid":1745531,"uid":114347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa5f7a042ef78d9d4e1ab0587c1779459604f6c5","tid":1745531,"uid":265179,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:20:15.000Z","msg":"以前一聽到汽油彈個名就好嚇人, 而家聽黎好似叉燒包咁好平常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:27:37.000Z","msg":"汽油彈只係用你平時生活可見嘅嘢嚟整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},